snippet.title: Fashion Dream - Start your dreamlike journey
snippet.description:
Dear Fashionistas,

Welcome to the most on trend 3D dress-up RPG game!
Are you ready to shine? Pick your favorite outfit out of thousands of fashion looks and dress up to be the next superstar!

Start you fashion journey ↓↓↓
App Store： https://apps.apple.com/ca/app/fashion-dream/id1530784011
Google Play：https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tencent.dressup

Don't forget to join our official community, and have fun with worldwide players!
■Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FashiondreamGlobal
■Discord: https://discord.gg/98QVtdvnND
